A MORTE DE FREDDY

7
00:01:07,231 --> 00:01:09,199
SPRINGWOOD, OHIO
DEZ ANOS ATRÁS

8
00:01:10,067 --> 00:01:12,365
MISTERIOSOS ASSASSINATOS
